text: Lautém is one of the municipalities of East Timor. Its capital is Lospalos. To the north lies the Banda Sea, and to the south the Timor Sea. Lautém includes the small island of Jaco. ==Administrative posts== The municipality's administrative posts (formerly sub-districts) are: *Iliomar *Lautém *Lospalos *Luro *Tutuala Category:Municipalities of East Timor
title: Lautém Municipality
